Title: New Electronic Musical Instruments Restoring the Relationship between Sound Source and Control  
Author: Bert Bongers 
Date: December 1996  
Note: 24 XOOTIC MAGAZINE  
Abstract: The relatively new way of producing sound by using analog or digital electronics offers an opportunity to devise new user interfaces or instrument forms. This article describes some of these controllers and explains more about the problems that occur in their development. Possible solutions are suggested. 
